|MCBFaeries are a race of woodland sprites, usually diminutive in stature.
This group encompasses brownies, dryads, atomies, sylphs and 
pixies, as well as sprites themselves.  They are known to be 
extremely agile as well as friendly and typically good-looking, but
due to their generally small size they are not very strong or sturdy.  
They have a reputation, deserved or not, for being pranksters, and 
tend to be a bit flighty at times.

|WKOFaeries cannot join the following guilds|RKB:
     Fighter, Garou, Morpher.
